data.description: Welcome Home!! All Upgrades Has Already Been Done! Just Move In & Enjoy This Beautiful Home! You Will Notice The Beautiful Manicured Lawn Soon As You Turn Into The Driveway; Super Clean 2-Car Garage; Gutter System That Channels Water Away From The House; Architectural Shingles; Huge Living Room w/ Gas Burning Fireplace; Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring Throughout Most Of The Home Downstairs; Formal Dining & Living Room, Huge Kitchen w/ Plenty Of Cabinet Space And Recessed Lighting; Open Concept; Stainless Steel Appliances Will Convey w/ Sale;  Master Bath Has Double Vanities, Separate Shower & Garden Tub; Huge Master Bedroom w/ French Doors Entry; Large Walk-In Closet; 2nd Bedroom -55" TV Will Convey w/ Sale; Also There Is A Sitting Area In The Closet For Some Quiet Reading; Great Room/Movie Room- Entertainment Center Will Convey w/ Sale! Dining Room Table & Chairs Will Remain; Decorative Accent Chest In The Kitchen Will Convey w/ Sale, Also, Study Desk will Convey; Large Back Porch For Outdoor Entertaining; Fenced Backyard; Huge Laundry Room w/ Shelving; Solar Panels- Buyer Must Assume Contract (Solar Panels are  $147.27 per month)  Architectural Shingles;  Washer & Dryer Will NOT Convey! VA Buyer's This Loan Is Assumable Provided You Get Approval From VA!! (Interest Rate 2.75%)
